lead_paragraph: Mwadi Mabika scored 19 points to lead the Los Angeles Sparks to a 73-63 victory over the host Liberty, handing the Liberty its season-high seventh loss in a row. Janel McCarville scored 16 points and Loree Moore had 10 for the Liberty (10-15).
